{"tid":1546842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應對近排天氣反覆無常","createTime":"2019-09-06T12:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T13:18:24.000Z","uid":281610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc4e1472ff915727f6ae039a02081be444516a8","tid":1546842,"uid":281610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"小弟有次返工突然落大雨，淋到變落湯雞，返到公司見到個同事乾到不得了，咁就問佢到底點解可以冇濕到啦，原來佢就着住件長袖雨褸加防水鞋袋。我見到近排成日落雨，搞到大家成身濕晒污糟晒，最慘仲要洗唔甩，啲衫褲鞋襪都要換過晒，就想上黎推薦大家上網用少少錢訂返啲長袖雨褸同防水鞋袋。我知大家可能唔係太接受買大陸野，不過都係用幾十蚊港紙，總好過花一大筆錢換過晒啲野，利申買咗幾套發夢用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=574297331851&amp;ali_refid=a3_430835_1006:1104778723:N:Ht3GHxxidarjFthkemdOqw%3D%3D:dfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f&amp;ali_trackid=1_dfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3D574297331851%26ali_refid%3Da3_430835_1006%3A1104778723%3AN%3AHt3GHxxidarjFthkemdOqw%253D%253D%3Adfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f%26ali_trackid%3D1_dfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d3278260\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=574297331851&amp;ali_refid=a3_430835_1006:1104778723:N:Ht3GHxxidarjFthkemdOqw%3D%3D:dfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f&amp;ali_trackid=1_dfd351caf117343595e5128dae1be85f</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=39149134214&amp;item_id=39149134214&amp;id=39149134214&amp;_fromTBWebVC=1&amp;item_id=39149134214&amp;spm=a21wu.11050243-global.list.1&amp;ttid=701287@htao_iphone_4.12.0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3D39149134214%26item_id%3D39149134214%26id%3D39149134214%26_fromTBWebVC%3D1%26item_id%3D39149134214%26spm%3Da21wu.11050243-global.list.1%26ttid%3D701287%40htao_iphone_4.12.0&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=e755ab44\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/